PrecisNATIONAL PAROLE BOARD (ADDITIONAL MEMBER) HONORARIUM REGULATIONS - which (a) fix the honorarium which is to be paid to persons selected from regional panels to act as additional members of the National Parole Board; and (b) revokes the Regulations made by Order in Council P.C. 1984-2967 of August 31, 1984.
